    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing exactly as it did the day it left the showroom. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and there are no chips, scratches, or imperfections to be found. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with the leather and trim showing zero signs of wear and still carrying that new-car scent. Mechanically, it is perfect, with all systems functioning exactly as intended and a comprehensive service history to prove its meticulous care.",
