    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is best suited for someone prioritizing utility and reliability over cosmetic perfection. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, a few small door dings, and some fading on the clear coat on the roof. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a small tear on the driver's side bolster, though all electronics remain functional. Mechanically, the car runs well, but it will likely need new tires and a brake service within the next few months. It has been a dependable vehicle, but it is priced to reflect its current cosmetic state and upcoming maintenance needs.",
