      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained in absolute showroom condition. This vehicle exhibits a level of preservation rarely seen on the market, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains in pristine, original state. Meticulously curated and mechanically peerless, this automobile offers an uncompromising driving experience for the most discerning collector. It stands as a testament to superior automotive stewardship and represents a premier acquisition opportunity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
